                  It is designed to utilize the users input about
                  <p>1) their goals </p>
                  <p>2) their emotions and </p>
                  <p>3) their trusted social network. Omnovi then gatherers and organizes the powerful influences from
                    the user’s Support Network. The Support Network’s messaging is delivered back to the user in text notes, pictures, audio and video format.
